title: Magic Constellations Wallpaper

creator: Mobile Visuals
descriptionHtml:
The visualizer creates a unique and cosmic soundscape, when it syncs with your music. The live wallpaper creates a journey with stars pulsating in many colors. New constellations appear all the time, so the journey will never end.

Music Visualizer

Play music with any audio app. Then switch to the music visualizer and it will visualize the sound. Moon Mission radio channel is available from the radio icon. A player for your music files is also included.

Background radio player

The radio can continue playing when this app is in the background. You can then do other things when you listen to the radio, like use other apps or exercise.

Create your own space music journey

Choose the distance between the constellations and the size and brightness of the stars. 20 music visualization themes and 8 backgrounds are included. 8 star types like "Alpha Centauri" and "Sirius" are available. Get temporary access to the settings in a simple way by watching a video ad. This access will last until you shut down the app.

17 constellations

These constellations and more are included:
Pleiadian clusters
Galactic eye
The all seeing eye
Passage to the other side of the universe
Spiral constellation
Cosmic eye
Ultra constellation
Wave constellation
Cosmic riddle
Elongated constellation
Elongated eye cluster
The "17 constellations"-feature is available from the settings.

Live wallpaper

Use the live wallpaper to personalize your phone.

Interactivity

You can adjust the speed with the + and – buttons on the visualizer.

PREMIUM FEATURES

3D-gyroscope

An interactive gyroscope is included, which makes it possible for you to control your ride through space.

Microphone visualization

You can visualize any sound from your phone's microphone. Visualize your own voice, music from your stereo or from a party. Microphone visualization has lots of possibilities.

Unlimited access to settings

You will have access to all of the settings and the constellations without having to watch any video ad.

RADIO CHANNELS IN THE FREE AND FULL VERSION

The radio channel comes from Moon mission:

https://www.internet-radio.com/station/mmr/

App video

The video is produced by Stefano Rodriguez. Watch other videos by him here:

https://www.youtube.com/user/TheStefanorodriguez
